<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٠٨٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4195">عُبَيْدِ اللهِ </a>قَالَ: أَخْبَرَنِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">عَبْدِ اللهِ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«صَلَّيْتُ مَعَ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> بِمِنًى رَكْعَتَيْنِ، وَأَبِي بَكْرٍ وَعُمَرَ، وَمَعَ عُثْمَانَ صَدْرًا مِنْ إِمَارَتِهِ ثُمَّ أَتَمَّهَا»</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>